lead_paragraph: Miami's Hassan Whiteside and Toronto's Jonas Valanciunas won't square off anymore in this Heat-Raptors Eastern Conference semifinal series.

headline.print_headline: Whiteside-Valanciunas Matchup Comes to an End After Injuries
